\c 54
\s Dhavhidhi anonyengetera kuti anunurwe pavavengi vake
\p Kumutungamiriri wekuimba; nemitengeranwa. Masikiri. \add Pisarema\add* raDhavhidhi. VaZifi pavakauya vakati kuna Sauro: Dhavhidhi haazinovanda kwatiri here?
\p
\v 1 Mwari, ndiponesei nezita renyu, uye nditongei nesimba renyu.
\v 2 Mwari, inzwai munyengetero wangu; ipai nzeve pamashoko emuromo wangu\x + Map. 55.1.\x*.
\v 3 Nokuti vatorwa vandimukira, uye vamanikidzi vanotsvaka mweya wangu. Havana kuisa Mwari pamberi pavo. Sera\x + Map. 18.44,45. 144.7. Map. 86.14.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Tarirai, Mwari mubatsiri wangu\x + Map. 118.7.\x*. Ishe ari pane vanotsigira mweya wangu\x + Map. 118.7.\x*.
\v 5 Achatsiva uipi kuvavengi vangu; vapedzei\x + Map. 89.49.\x* muchokwadi chenyu\x + Map. 143.12.\x*.
\v 6 Ndichakubairai chipo nekuzvidira\x + Num.. 15.3. Map. 51.12. Hos. 14.4.\x*; ndicharumbidza zita renyu, Jehovha, nokuti rakanaka\x + Map. 52.9.\x*.
\v 7 Nokuti wakandinunura kubva mudambudziko rose; uye ziso rangu rakaona \add chishuwo changu\add* pavavengi vangu\x + Map. 59.10. 92.11. 112.8. 118.7.\x*.
